| ------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| `loom-senior-software-engineer` | **DEFAULT.** All work requiring judgment: implementation, architecture, bugs, debugging, verification, refactoring, test strategy |
| `loom-software-engineer`        | ONLY: unit tests for existing code, boilerplate with detailed instructions, scaffolding from concrete plan |
| `loom-code-reviewer`            | Read-only code/security/architecture review                                                  |
| `Explore` agent                 | Codebase exploration                                                                         |
| Domain skills                   | See Skills by Domain table below                                                             |

**Note:** `loom-software-engineer` can write unit tests but verification (proving end-to-end wiring) requires `loom-senior-software-engineer`.

#### Skills by Domain

| Domain                  | Skills                                                                                        |
| ----------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Security & Auth         | `/loom-auth` — OAuth2, JWT, RBAC/ABAC, session management, MFA                                |
| Testing                 | `/loom-testing` — Unit, integration, e2e, security tests, TDD/BDD, coverage                    |
