## STANDARD RULES

### 15. QUALITY GATES

Zero lint errors, tests passing, self-reviewed for security before completion. **Nothing is "pre-existing"** — every warning and failure you see is YOUR responsibility.

### 16. DEPENDENCIES

Never hand-edit manifests. Use: `bun add`, `cargo add`, `uv add`, `go get`

### 17. CODE SIZE LIMITS

File: 400 lines | Function: 50 lines | Class: 300 lines — Exceed = refactor immediately.

### 18. SESSION STATE & KNOWLEDGE PLACEMENT

System knowledge belongs in `doc/loom/knowledge/` via `loom knowledge update`. Do NOT modify the project's CLAUDE.md.

